Package: gsDesignTune
Title: Dependency-Aware Scenario Exploration for Group Sequential Designs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nan", "Xiao", email = "me@nanx.me", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0250-5673")))
Description: Systematic, dependency-aware exploration of group sequential
    designs created by 'gsDesign::gsDesign()' and 'gsDesign::gsSurv()'.
    Provides reproducible grid/random search over user-defined candidate sets,
    parallel evaluation via the 'future' framework, standardized metric
    extraction, and auditable reporting for design-space evaluation and
    trade-off analysis.
